dc_title_s: Chart prepared by James B. Moore to accompany his memorial to Congress respecting the subject of steam communication with China, Japan & c, 1850.
dc_description_s: Inset: Harbour of San Francisco, California. Tables of distances. Shows distances between major ports of the world. 1 map; 71 x 96 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
